1
00:07:40,140 --> 00:07:42,380
<font color="yellow">(Episode 15)</font>

2
00:07:42,820 --> 00:07:51,820
<font color="yellow">BioskopKeren</font>

3
00:07:52,380 --> 00:07:54,140
<font color="yellow">Oh, you again.</font>

4
00:07:54,860 --> 00:07:56,060
<font color="yellow">I'll say.</font>

5
00:08:11,140 --> 00:08:12,500
<font color="yellow">"I'll say"?</font>

6
00:08:13,340 --> 00:08:15,340
<font color="yellow">Is that what I just said?</font>

7
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:21,500
<font color="yellow">Wait!</font>

8
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:41,380
<font color="yellow">Lady.</font>

9
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:47,180
<font color="yellow">- Me? - It's good to see you here.</font>

10
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:50,580
<font color="yellow">- Do you know me? - No.</font>

11
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:53,780
<font color="yellow">But that necklace you're wearing.</font>

12
00:08:56,980 --> 00:08:59,300
<font color="yellow">- This? - I made that.</font>

13
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:02,340
<font color="yellow">A man asked me to design it.</font>

14
00:09:02,340 --> 00:09:04,900
<font color="yellow">Must have been 10 years ago.</font>

15
00:09:09,220 --> 00:09:11,900
<font color="yellow">10 years? What man?</font>

16
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:13,100
<font color="yellow">You should know better.</font>

17
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:15,260
<font color="yellow">You're the owner of the necklace.</font>

18
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:17,100
<font color="yellow">Do you know what it means?</font>

19
00:09:18,180 --> 00:09:19,820
<font color="yellow">- No. - It means...</font>

20
00:09:19,820 --> 00:09:22,900
<font color="yellow">"a match made in Heaven" in French.</font>

21
00:09:24,060 --> 00:09:27,820
<font color="yellow">Destiny made outside of man's boundary.</font>

22
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:32,140
<font color="yellow">Are you living happily with the man who gave you that necklace?</font>

23
00:10:21,740 --> 00:10:24,740
<font color="yellow">Will you stop? You're out of places to try.</font>

24
00:10:24,740 --> 00:10:27,020
<font color="yellow">There's one place I haven't tried.</font>

25
00:10:28,300 --> 00:10:29,860
<font color="yellow">The place she's at.</font>

26
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:32,900
<font color="yellow">Then go. I give my permission.</font>

27
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:34,220
<font color="yellow">Can I go?</font>

28
00:10:35,060 --> 00:10:38,180
<font color="yellow">Would it be okay to cause her confusion?</font>

29
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:42,060
<font color="yellow">Is it okay to confuse me? I'm on edge because of you.</font>

30
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:45,580
<font color="yellow">I feel so empty inside.</font>

31
00:10:55,060 --> 00:10:56,260
<font color="yellow">Are you crazy?</font>

32
00:11:04,300 --> 00:11:06,740
<font color="yellow">He lived for a long time, too.</font>

33
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:10,100
<font color="yellow">Put that back before you cause an international dispute.</font>

34
00:11:12,180 --> 00:11:13,780
<font color="yellow">He wants us gone.</font>

35
00:11:13,900 --> 00:11:15,740
<font color="yellow">He's scary when he's angry.</font>

36
00:11:24,900 --> 00:11:27,940
<font color="yellow">Gosh, this is just so weird.</font>

37
00:11:27,940 --> 00:11:29,740
<font color="yellow">How could we meet here?</font>

38
00:11:30,060 --> 00:11:32,820
<font color="yellow">I'm on a business trip. I'm here to research...</font>

39
00:11:32,820 --> 00:11:35,100
<font color="yellow">designs to put on the corners of our furniture.</font>

40
00:11:35,100 --> 00:11:37,340
<font color="yellow">- What are you on about? - I don't know.</font>

41
00:11:39,620 --> 00:11:41,020
<font color="yellow">How have you been?</font>

42
00:11:44,900 --> 00:11:47,620
<font color="yellow">Are you following me?</font>

43
00:11:47,620 --> 00:11:49,140
<font color="yellow">Is that a crime?</font>

44
00:11:49,620 --> 00:11:51,540
<font color="yellow">- What should I do? - I'm not a bad man.</font>

45
00:11:51,540 --> 00:11:52,620
<font color="yellow">How would I know that?</font>

46
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:53,980
<font color="yellow">By spending time with me.</font>

47
00:11:53,980 --> 00:11:55,140
<font color="yellow">I have no reason to do that.</font>

48
00:11:55,140 --> 00:11:57,420
<font color="yellow">My company sponsored your radio show.</font>

49
00:11:57,420 --> 00:11:59,580
<font color="yellow">You offered to buy me a meal.</font>

50
00:12:02,500 --> 00:12:04,780
<font color="yellow">Is this your first time in Canada?</font>

51
00:12:04,780 --> 00:12:06,900
<font color="yellow">Let's go this way.</font>

52
00:12:14,220 --> 00:12:17,580
<font color="yellow">Did I tell you I'd be in Canada?</font>

53
00:12:17,580 --> 00:12:21,100
<font color="yellow">- Didn't I just say I'd go abroad? - I think you mentioned Canada.</font>

54
00:12:21,100 --> 00:12:23,860
<font color="yellow">You said something about maple leaves.</font>

55
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:25,220
<font color="yellow">Maple leaves?</font>

56
00:12:26,540 --> 00:12:28,140
<font color="yellow">I remember that.</font>

57
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:31,580
<font color="yellow">Let's go this way.</font>

58
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:49,220
<font color="yellow">Is this enough?</font>

59
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:52,580
<font color="yellow">It's fine.</font>

60
00:12:52,580 --> 00:12:54,940
<font color="yellow">It's nice like we're on a picnic.</font>

61
00:12:55,060 --> 00:12:56,980
<font color="yellow">Not for you, for me.</font>

62
00:12:57,500 --> 00:12:59,100
<font color="yellow">Is this enough for me?</font>

63
00:12:59,540 --> 00:13:01,900
<font color="yellow">Remember how much I sponsored your show with?</font>

64
00:13:07,820 --> 00:13:09,140
<font color="yellow">The thing is,</font>

65
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:12,820
<font color="yellow">this trip was sudden, not planned.</font>

66
00:13:13,100 --> 00:13:15,820
<font color="yellow">I didn't bring that much money.</font>

67
00:13:16,220 --> 00:13:18,060
<font color="yellow">- What do you like? - Beef.</font>

68
00:13:19,900 --> 00:13:22,300
<font color="yellow">I'm not much of a meat-eater.</font>

69
00:13:22,300 --> 00:13:23,740
<font color="yellow">You love it.</font>

70
00:13:29,100 --> 00:13:30,300
<font color="yellow">How do you know that?</font>

71
00:13:31,620 --> 00:13:34,140
<font color="yellow">Well... Who doesn't like meat?</font>

72
00:13:34,140 --> 00:13:36,060
<font color="yellow">Don't avoid my question.</font>

73
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:39,380
<font color="yellow">Did you have someone dig up my information?</font>

74
00:13:39,380 --> 00:13:41,580
<font color="yellow">To find out if my family...</font>

75
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:43,900
<font color="yellow">is on par with yours?</font>

76
00:13:44,500 --> 00:13:46,300
<font color="yellow">Who said I'd date you?</font>

77
00:13:46,300 --> 00:13:48,300
<font color="yellow">You're not a catch at all.</font>

78
00:13:50,540 --> 00:13:52,060
<font color="yellow">You need to buy me meat.</font>

79
00:13:55,380 --> 00:13:56,780
<font color="yellow">That should taste lovely.</font>

80
00:13:56,980 --> 00:13:59,740
<font color="yellow">I'll call you later. Bye.</font>

81
00:14:11,220 --> 00:14:13,380
<font color="yellow">There's nothing much this way. Go that way.</font>

82
00:14:13,380 --> 00:14:14,940
<font color="yellow">I'll show you around.</font>

83
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:19,540
<font color="yellow">Can you do that?</font>

84
00:14:21,140 --> 00:14:23,660
<font color="yellow">I don't want to be a nuisance.</font>

85
00:14:23,740 --> 00:14:27,060
<font color="yellow">It's okay. I'm sure you did it out of excitement.</font>

86
00:14:36,940 --> 00:14:39,340
<font color="yellow">You seem to know Quebec well.</font>

87
00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:40,860
<font color="yellow">Were you here before?</font>

88
00:14:41,980 --> 00:14:45,100
<font color="yellow">Yes. I was here with my first love.</font>

89
00:14:48,300 --> 00:14:50,060
<font color="yellow">We came here four times.</font>

90
00:14:53,540 --> 00:14:55,380
<font color="yellow">You have a girlfriend, then.</font>

91
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:57,620
<font color="yellow">Not anymore.</font>

92
00:14:57,620 --> 00:14:59,380
<font color="yellow">Why did you break up?</font>

93
00:15:01,740 --> 00:15:05,580
<font color="yellow">I was very far away for a very long time.</font>

94
00:15:06,740 --> 00:15:08,260
<font color="yellow">It took a toll on her.</font>

95
00:15:09,100 --> 00:15:10,740
<font color="yellow">She'd forgotten all about me.</font>

96
00:15:10,820 --> 00:15:13,900
<font color="yellow">First loves never work out.</font>

97
00:15:15,580 --> 00:15:17,300
<font color="yellow">You must've loved her a lot.</font>

98
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:23,740
<font color="yellow">I guess I did, considering I can't hold back.</font>

99
00:15:24,940 --> 00:15:26,580
<font color="yellow">What are you holding back?</font>

100
00:15:31,300 --> 00:15:32,860
<font color="yellow">I want to hold her hand...</font>

101
00:15:33,620 --> 00:15:35,540
<font color="yellow">and hold her close.</font>

102
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:40,620
<font color="yellow">The woman forgot about you...</font>

103
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:43,220
<font color="yellow">but you didn't forget her.</font>

104
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:45,940
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

105
00:15:46,940 --> 00:15:49,180
<font color="yellow">Never for a second or a day.</font>

106
00:15:51,820 --> 00:15:53,820
<font color="yellow">What a lucky woman.</font>

107
00:15:57,300 --> 00:15:58,740
<font color="yellow">Have you heard?</font>

108
00:15:59,180 --> 00:16:00,780
<font color="yellow">If you catch a falling maple leaf,</font>

109
00:16:00,780 --> 00:16:03,500
<font color="yellow">you fall in love with the person you're with.</font>

110
00:16:06,580 --> 00:16:09,020
<font color="yellow">Is that what your first love said?</font>

111
00:16:09,740 --> 00:16:11,820
<font color="yellow">Yes, and I caught a leaf.</font>

112
00:16:11,820 --> 00:16:14,660
<font color="yellow">Do you still believe that? It didn't work out for you.</font>

113
00:16:14,660 --> 00:16:17,540
<font color="yellow">You're here with me because it didn't work out.</font>

114
00:16:17,540 --> 00:16:19,580
<font color="yellow">And you have a thing for me.</font>

115
00:16:19,620 --> 00:16:22,580
<font color="yellow">Men can be really silly. They tell the woman they like...</font>

116
00:16:22,660 --> 00:16:24,100
<font color="yellow">about their exes.</font>

117
00:16:25,700 --> 00:16:27,580
<font color="yellow">- Is that so? - Isn't it?</font>

118
00:16:32,100 --> 00:16:34,140
<font color="yellow">Are you an idiot? A teenager?</font>

119
00:16:34,140 --> 00:16:36,260
<font color="yellow">Do you believe catching a leaf makes you fall in love?</font>

120
00:16:36,260 --> 00:16:38,780
<font color="yellow">He fell for that woman's tricks.</font>

121
00:16:38,780 --> 00:16:40,580
<font color="yellow">He's such an idiot.</font>

122
00:16:43,540 --> 00:16:45,780
<font color="yellow">(You are his bride.)</font>

123
00:16:46,260 --> 00:16:47,900
<font color="yellow">Who are you?</font>

124
00:16:47,900 --> 00:16:51,340
<font color="yellow">Are you living happily with the man who gave you that necklace?</font>

125
00:16:51,700 --> 00:16:53,620
<font color="yellow">I don't remember anything.</font>

126
00:16:54,620 --> 00:16:58,420
<font color="yellow">I don't even know which chunk of my memories I lost.</font>

127
00:17:12,780 --> 00:17:13,900
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

128
00:17:16,740 --> 00:17:18,740
<font color="yellow">I don't remember anything.</font>

129
00:17:18,740 --> 00:17:20,220
<font color="yellow">Nothing at all.</font>

130
00:17:20,940 --> 00:17:22,500
<font color="yellow">Let's just go and ask.</font>

131
00:17:22,940 --> 00:17:24,100
<font color="yellow">That should be quicker.</font>

132
00:17:28,740 --> 00:17:30,140
<font color="yellow">Why are you here?</font>

133
00:17:30,380 --> 00:17:31,820
<font color="yellow">Are you staying here?</font>

134
00:17:32,980 --> 00:17:34,580
<font color="yellow">- Yes. - I see.</font>

135
00:17:37,020 --> 00:17:38,540
<font color="yellow">I have a question.</font>

136
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:40,380
<font color="yellow">Did we...</font>

137
00:17:43,020 --> 00:17:44,900
<font color="yellow">meet somewhere before?</font>

138
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:47,580
<font color="yellow">About 10 years ago?</font>

139
00:17:48,140 --> 00:17:49,620
<font color="yellow">Mister.</font>

140
00:17:56,060 --> 00:17:59,100
<font color="yellow">It's a bit weird but I'm not hitting on you.</font>

141
00:18:00,380 --> 00:18:03,100
<font color="yellow">I keep having this weird feeling.</font>

142
00:18:13,100 --> 00:18:14,620
<font color="yellow">Do you like me?</font>

143
00:18:15,020 --> 00:18:17,900
<font color="yellow">No. I said I'm not hitting on you.</font>

144
00:18:21,420 --> 00:18:22,620
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

145
00:18:24,700 --> 00:18:25,980
<font color="yellow">You're my type.</font>

146
00:18:27,220 --> 00:18:28,540
<font color="yellow">For your information,</font>

147
00:18:29,340 --> 00:18:31,180
<font color="yellow">I don't have a boyfriend.</font>

148
00:18:31,940 --> 00:18:35,340
<font color="yellow">I'm not very lucky with men in this life.</font>

149
00:18:41,060 --> 00:18:42,660
<font color="yellow">I'm just saying.</font>

150
00:18:43,380 --> 00:18:44,660
<font color="yellow">I'll get going then.</font>

151
00:18:45,140 --> 00:18:46,500
<font color="yellow">Have a nice walk.</font>

152
00:18:48,180 --> 00:18:49,740
<font color="yellow">- Excuse me. - Excuse me.</font>

153
00:18:58,060 --> 00:18:59,340
<font color="yellow">You go first.</font>

154
00:19:02,380 --> 00:19:03,580
<font color="yellow">You were right.</font>

155
00:19:03,820 --> 00:19:06,140
<font color="yellow">A sandwich wasn't enough.</font>

156
00:19:06,580 --> 00:19:08,900
<font color="yellow">Why don't we have early dinner? Aren't you hungry?</font>

157
00:19:10,060 --> 00:19:11,420
<font color="yellow">It will be my treat.</font>

158
00:19:13,140 --> 00:19:15,420
<font color="yellow">I was going to ask you out for dinner too.</font>

159
00:19:15,900 --> 00:19:17,540
<font color="yellow">I know a restaurant that serves good beef.</font>

160
00:19:18,380 --> 00:19:19,500
<font color="yellow">Beef.</font>

161
00:19:19,780 --> 00:19:21,580
<font color="yellow">I was thoughtless.</font>

162
00:19:21,580 --> 00:19:24,380
<font color="yellow">My feet hurt like crazy because I didn't bring my sneakers.</font>

163
00:19:24,420 --> 00:19:26,420
<font color="yellow">Your feet might hurt, but you must look beautiful.</font>

164
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:27,780
<font color="yellow">It's okay.</font>

165
00:19:27,780 --> 00:19:30,420
<font color="yellow">At least you now know that you have to take sneakers with you next time.</font>

166
00:19:30,620 --> 00:19:33,140
<font color="yellow">I know. It's not like I've been abroad before.</font>

167
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:34,420
<font color="yellow">I know.</font>

168
00:19:34,420 --> 00:19:36,700
<font color="yellow">Why would you go there now when you're just about to turn 30?</font>

169
00:19:36,980 --> 00:19:40,260
<font color="yellow">When I was 29, I didn't even travel as far as to the corner store.</font>

170
00:19:40,260 --> 00:19:42,300
<font color="yellow">Really? Thank you.</font>

171
00:19:42,300 --> 00:19:44,580
<font color="yellow">I didn't have any appointments.</font>

172
00:19:44,580 --> 00:19:47,060
<font color="yellow">I've been traveling around just fine...</font>

173
00:19:47,060 --> 00:19:48,820
<font color="yellow">for someone who's never been abroad before.</font>

174
00:19:49,060 --> 00:19:51,220
<font color="yellow">I rarely get lost and I never miss a meal.</font>

175
00:19:51,220 --> 00:19:53,060
<font color="yellow">Now, I'm going to have a big chunk of beef.</font>

176
00:19:53,380 --> 00:19:58,060
<font color="yellow">I'm at a nice restaurant with some man.</font>

177
00:19:58,060 --> 00:20:01,700
<font color="yellow">It's the man that has to be nice, not the restaurant.</font>

178
00:20:01,740 --> 00:20:03,540
<font color="yellow">I have to go. I'm sleepy.</font>

179
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:06,020
<font color="yellow">Okay. Have a good night.</font>

180
00:20:08,220 --> 00:20:10,220
<font color="yellow">The future I saw was right.</font>

181
00:20:11,780 --> 00:20:13,140
<font color="yellow">Over here, Sir.</font>

182
00:20:14,500 --> 00:20:17,580
<font color="yellow">You ended up meeting this guy.</font>

183
00:20:18,940 --> 00:20:21,900
<font color="yellow">I'm embarrassed that I can't stop smiling.</font>

184
00:20:39,060 --> 00:20:40,740
<font color="yellow">Did you come here...</font>

185
00:20:40,900 --> 00:20:42,900
<font color="yellow">with your first love too?</font>

186
00:20:45,340 --> 00:20:47,500
<font color="yellow">You fed her a really expensive meal.</font>

187
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:50,060
<font color="yellow">It was useless though. She forgot all about it.</font>

188
00:20:50,780 --> 00:20:52,740
<font color="yellow">Did you see her even after breaking up?</font>

189
00:20:53,140 --> 00:20:54,220
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

190
00:21:00,980 --> 00:21:03,300
<font color="yellow">I heard that the memory about first love often gets glamorized...</font>

191
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:05,900
<font color="yellow">and you get disappointed when you meet again.</font>

192
00:21:06,580 --> 00:21:08,140
<font color="yellow">No, it's not true. She's still beautiful.</font>

193
00:21:08,140 --> 00:21:09,340
<font color="yellow">Excuse me.</font>

194
00:21:10,060 --> 00:21:11,980
<font color="yellow">I'm going to order. Are you ready to order?</font>

195
00:21:12,940 --> 00:21:14,020
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

196
00:21:14,740 --> 00:21:16,580
<font color="yellow">- I will... - What do you think about...</font>

197
00:21:16,580 --> 00:21:17,980
<font color="yellow">a girl who just became quite beautiful?</font>

198
00:21:17,980 --> 00:21:20,900
<font color="yellow">I recently became quite beautiful. Of course that's what I think.</font>

199
00:21:23,700 --> 00:21:25,340
<font color="yellow">Can we meet again tomorrow?</font>

200
00:21:30,060 --> 00:21:31,500
<font color="yellow">I'm flying out tomorrow afternoon.</font>

201
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:32,700
<font color="yellow">Before you go.</font>

202
00:21:33,060 --> 00:21:34,220
<font color="yellow">And also in Korea.</font>

203
00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:53,380
<font color="yellow">Welcome.</font>

204
00:21:56,140 --> 00:21:57,980
<font color="yellow">She won't be here today, either.</font>

205
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:01,660
<font color="yellow">Just give her this.</font>

206
00:22:03,300 --> 00:22:07,060
<font color="yellow">No wonder I wanted to go to work all of a sudden.</font>

207
00:22:13,980 --> 00:22:15,380
<font color="yellow">Are you...</font>

208
00:22:23,900 --> 00:22:25,140
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

209
00:22:25,620 --> 00:22:27,220
<font color="yellow">Are you the one who's been looking for me?</font>

210
00:22:27,220 --> 00:22:29,740
<font color="yellow">Yes. You are Yu Deok Hwa, right?</font>

211
00:22:29,780 --> 00:22:31,140
<font color="yellow">The previous owner of the building.</font>

212
00:22:31,140 --> 00:22:32,980
<font color="yellow">Do you remember the chicken restaurant on the first floor?</font>

213
00:22:32,980 --> 00:22:33,980
<font color="yellow">Nine years ago.</font>

214
00:22:33,980 --> 00:22:36,540
<font color="yellow">I remember of course. You never paid rent on time.</font>

215
00:22:36,540 --> 00:22:38,900
<font color="yellow">Why were you looking for me?</font>

216
00:22:39,980 --> 00:22:42,060
