00:49:43,420 --> 00:49:47,100
<font color="yellow">than 70 years.</font>

532
00:50:41,860 --> 00:50:43,060
<font color="yellow">Sorry.</font>

533
00:50:44,060 --> 00:50:45,540
<font color="yellow">I'm very late.</font>

534
00:50:49,300 --> 00:50:51,660
