564
00:52:52,300 --> 00:52:54,300
<font color="yellow">May I just call you "Grim Reaper" now?</font>

565
00:52:55,900 --> 00:52:57,420
<font color="yellow">Missing Soul.</font>

566
00:52:58,780 --> 00:53:00,900
<font color="yellow">She really is an unexpected guest.</font>

567
00:53:02,940 --> 00:53:04,740
<font color="yellow">She remembered everything.</font>

568
00:53:04,820 --> 00:53:06,220
<font color="yellow">She recognized me.</font>

569
00:53:08,060 --> 00:53:09,260
