570
00:53:09,260 --> 00:53:11,700
<font color="yellow">I haven't heard that in so long.</font>

571
00:53:11,740 --> 00:53:13,340
<font color="yellow">I heard everything.</font>

572
00:53:13,340 --> 00:53:16,220
<font color="yellow">How could you not come once when you remembered everything?</font>

573
00:53:16,220 --> 00:53:19,300
<font color="yellow">What good could seeing a grim reaper bring to a human?</font>

574
00:53:19,620 --> 00:53:21,420
<font color="yellow">It's been a while.</font>

575
00:53:21,420 --> 00:53:22,820
<font color="yellow">I've been enjoying your radio show.</font>

576
00:53:22,820 --> 00:53:26,060
<font color="yellow">It's been way too long to say it's been a while.</font>

577
00:53:26,060 --> 00:53:28,700
<font color="yellow">I'm already 29 years old.</font>

578
00:53:30,620 --> 00:53:31,820
<font color="yellow">29.</font>

579
00:53:33,580 --> 00:53:34,860
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

