00:53:36,100 --> 00:53:38,260
<font color="yellow">Let's eat. Wash your hands.</font>

581
00:53:55,660 --> 00:53:57,380
<font color="yellow">Shall I tell you a secret?</font>

582
00:53:57,420 --> 00:53:58,540
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

583
00:53:59,260 --> 00:54:03,340
<font color="yellow">You will meet a grim reaper when you are 29.</font>

584
00:54:03,820 --> 00:54:05,300
<font color="yellow">Even if it's not me.</font>

585
00:54:06,220 --> 00:54:08,540
<font color="yellow">That's the fate of a missing soul.</font>

586
00:54:09,780 --> 00:54:11,820
<font color="yellow">This world requires order...</font>

587
00:54:12,260 --> 00:54:13,620
<font color="yellow">and nine...</font>

588
00:54:13,940 --> 00:54:16,140
<font color="yellow">is the closest lower number to 10,</font>

589
00:54:16,140 --> 00:54:19,380
<font color="yellow">a perfect number that symbolizes the almighty.</font>

590
00:54:20,660 --> 00:54:21,940
<font color="yellow">I wish you luck then...</font>

591
00:54:22,260 --> 00:54:23,500
<font color="yellow">as well.</font>

592
00:54:24,260 --> 00:54:25,660
<font color="yellow">You met me...</font>

593
00:54:27,660 --> 00:54:30,140
<font color="yellow">at the age of 29 as well.</font>

594
00:54:34,260 --> 00:54:35,820
<font color="yellow">You met a grim reaper.</font>

595
00:54:38,060 --> 00:54:41,660
<font color="yellow">Eun Tak, it hasn't been a month yet.</font>

596
00:54:42,300 --> 00:54:44,900
<font color="yellow">Are the symptoms...</font>

597
00:54:45,140 --> 00:54:48,100
<font color="yellow">No. I came to say bye...</font>

598
00:54:48,180 --> 00:54:50,700
<font color="yellow">and to thank you for everything.</font>

599
00:54:51,060 --> 00:54:52,700
<font color="yellow">Thank you...</font>

600
00:54:52,940 --> 00:54:55,660
<font color="yellow">for keeping me alive.</font>

601
00:54:55,700 --> 00:54:59,180
<font color="yellow">Otherwise, I would've been very miserable.</font>

602
00:54:59,180 --> 00:55:03,140
<font color="yellow">I finally remembered how to be happy.</font>

603
00:55:03,140 --> 00:55:04,660
<font color="yellow">That's great.</font>

604
00:55:05,180 --> 00:55:06,500
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

605
00:55:06,660 --> 00:55:08,540
<font color="yellow">what is that method?</font>

606
00:55:19,300 --> 00:55:20,980
<font color="yellow">I smell meat.</font>

607
00:55:21,060 --> 00:55:22,940
<font color="yellow">Your taste hasn't changed.</font>

608
00:55:23,500 --> 00:55:25,700
<font color="yellow">I have the pan on the stove.</font>

609
00:55:25,700 --> 00:55:28,020
<font color="yellow">Hold on. Oh, did you eat yet?</font>

610
00:55:28,020 --> 00:55:29,700
<font color="yellow">If not, eat with me.</font>

611
00:55:47,820 --> 00:55:50,300
<font color="yellow">You're holding the same book you were holding nine years ago.</font>

612
00:55:50,300 --> 00:55:52,300
<font color="yellow">When will you finish reading that?</font>

613
00:55:53,220 --> 00:55:56,580
<font color="yellow">A man reads and writes the same book 100 times.</font>

614
00:55:57,860 --> 00:55:59,620
<font color="yellow">Look at you lie.</font>

615
00:55:59,740 --> 00:56:01,060
<font color="yellow">How cute.</font>

616
00:56:02,860 --> 00:56:04,540
<font color="yellow">- Is it obvious? - Yes.</font>

617
00:56:13,740 --> 00:56:15,620
<font color="yellow">What is this? Where am I?</font>

618
00:56:17,580 --> 00:56:19,300
<font color="yellow">Under the blanket.</font>

619
00:56:20,380 --> 00:56:23,300
<font color="yellow">You're really vulgar.</font>

620
00:56:24,900 --> 00:56:26,660
<font color="yellow">Leave if you don't feel like it.</font>

621
00:56:29,660 --> 00:56:31,140
<font color="yellow">It's so warm.</font>

622
00:56:31,780 --> 00:56:34,060
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

623
00:56:35,820 --> 00:56:38,180
<font color="yellow">Now that I'm warm I feel sleepy.</font>

624
00:56:50,260 --> 00:56:54,180
<font color="yellow">One, two, three...</font>

625
00:56:54,700 --> 00:56:57,300
<font color="yellow">Four, five...</font>

626
00:56:57,660 --> 00:56:58,740
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

627
00:57:05,620 --> 00:57:07,500
<font color="yellow">I was so scared.</font>

628
00:57:08,500 --> 00:57:10,300
<font color="yellow">Scared that it's a dream.</font>

629
00:57:10,660 --> 00:57:12,740
<font color="yellow">That I'm still dreaming.</font>

630
00:57:15,020 --> 00:57:16,420
<font color="yellow">It's not a dream.</font>

631
00:57:16,900 --> 00:57:18,900
<font color="yellow">You scared me.</font>

632
00:57:20,700 --> 00:57:24,380
<font color="yellow">From now on, show up before I count to three.</font>

633
00:57:25,700 --> 00:57:28,700
<font color="yellow">Don't go anywhere, okay?</font>

634
00:57:29,660 --> 00:57:32,300
<font color="yellow">Okay, I won't go anywhere.</font>

635
00:57:32,820 --> 00:57:34,020
<font color="yellow">Get in bed.</font>

636
00:57:39,820 --> 00:57:41,660
<font color="yellow">You left me once.</font>

637
00:57:51,500 --> 00:57:52,780
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

638
00:58:17,420 --> 00:58:18,940
<font color="yellow">You, over there.</font>

639
00:58:27,900 --> 00:58:32,140
<font color="yellow">Why did you leave Eun Tak's room to stare into mine?</font>

640
00:58:36,140 --> 00:58:37,620
<font color="yellow">Are you Mr. Restaurant?</font>

641
00:58:38,260 --> 00:58:39,580
<font color="yellow">Mr. Restaurant?</font>

642
00:58:52,700 --> 00:58:54,540
<font color="yellow">So that's what happens.</font>

643
00:58:56,060 --> 00:58:58,420
<font color="yellow">You choose that path in the end.</font>

644
00:58:59,900 --> 00:59:01,980
<font color="yellow">It is good to see you smile.</font>

645
00:59:02,580 --> 00:59:05,900
<font color="yellow">Who's smiling? Should I smile right now?</font>

646
00:59:07,300 --> 00:59:09,660
<font color="yellow">Your temperament has not changed at all.</font>

647
00:59:09,780 --> 00:59:14,180
<font color="yellow">Maybe not now, but you smile in the end, so all is well.</font>

648
00:59:22,220 --> 00:59:24,500
<font color="yellow">Where are you going dressed like that?</font>

649
00:59:25,140 --> 00:59:27,700
<font color="yellow">Are you actually leaving? Hey.</font>

650
00:59:35,180 --> 00:59:36,700
<font color="yellow">Make my part-timer...</font>

651
00:59:37,620 --> 00:59:39,980
<font color="yellow">a happy woman.</font>

652
00:59:40,820 --> 00:59:42,980
<font color="yellow">Your foolish little sister...</font>

653
00:59:44,380 --> 00:59:46,500
<font color="yellow">will be happy as well.</font>

654
00:59:52,940 --> 00:59:56,020
<font color="yellow">Where did he go so early in the morning? Scalpel.</font>

655
01:00:01,980 --> 01:00:03,020
<font color="yellow">Uncle Tenant.</font>

656
01:00:03,140 --> 01:00:05,140
<font color="yellow">What's that watch? I want it.</font>

657
01:00:05,580 --> 01:00:07,740
<font color="yellow">Time is everything in my line of work.</font>

658
01:00:08,060 --> 01:00:10,540
<font color="yellow">A grim reaper prefers black.</font>

659
01:00:10,780 --> 01:00:13,420
<font color="yellow">I like it. This is your breakfast. Do you like it?</font>

660
01:00:14,260 --> 01:00:15,820
<font color="yellow">There you go again.</font>

661
01:00:16,180 --> 01:00:18,700
<font color="yellow">You're still so careless.</font>

662
01:00:18,980 --> 01:00:21,180
<font color="yellow">Do you even know what you're saying?</font>

663
01:00:21,300 --> 01:00:23,580
<font color="yellow">He just found you out.</font>

664
01:00:24,500 --> 01:00:26,500
<font color="yellow">I found out about you first.</font>

665
01:00:26,500 --> 01:00:28,860
<font color="yellow">You had blue flames all over you when you came over.</font>

666
01:00:29,500 --> 01:00:30,740
<font color="yellow">I thought it was spontaneous combustion.</font>

667
01:00:30,820 --> 01:00:33,340
<font color="yellow">You careless goblin.</font>

668
01:00:34,580 --> 01:00:38,300
<font color="yellow">Deok Hwa, it'll be hard to believe, but you should know the truth.</font>

669
01:00:38,300 --> 01:00:39,420
<font color="yellow">About what?</font>

670
01:00:39,940 --> 01:00:42,740
<font color="yellow">That he's a goblin and you're a grim reaper?</font>

671
01:00:43,540 --> 01:00:46,300
<font color="yellow">- How do you know that? - We just told him.</font>

672
01:00:46,980 --> 01:00:48,300
<font color="yellow">Oh, right.</font>

673
01:00:48,660 --> 01:00:52,100
<font color="yellow">I don't understand why you aren't shocked.</font>

674
01:00:52,100 --> 01:00:54,820
<font color="yellow">Grandpa told me ever since I turned six.</font>

675
01:00:54,980 --> 01:00:56,980
<font color="yellow">That I have an uncle who's a goblin.</font>

676
01:00:57,020 --> 01:00:59,940
<font color="yellow">That our family served that goblin for generations.</font>

677
01:01:00,140 --> 01:01:02,580
<font color="yellow">I thought it was some kind of odd religion.</font>

678
01:01:02,620 --> 01:01:05,060
<font color="yellow">I never imagined he meant a literal goblin.</font>

679
01:01:05,060 --> 01:01:08,180
<font color="yellow">I understand. It would be hard to imagine.</font>

680
01:01:08,180 --> 01:01:09,700
<font color="yellow">Prove it.</font>

681
01:01:10,580 --> 01:01:14,380
<font color="yellow">Prove it if you can. Both of you, if you please.</font>

682
01:01:18,980 --> 01:01:20,060
<font color="yellow">How was that?</font>

683
01:01:24,540 --> 01:01:27,300
<font color="yellow">Ever seen psychokinesis at work? What do you think?</font>

684
01:01:27,300 --> 01:01:29,500
<font color="yellow">Even humans can do that.</font>

685
01:01:29,620 --> 01:01:31,220
<font color="yellow">Don't you know David Copperfield?</font>

686
01:01:32,580 --> 01:01:33,700
<font color="yellow">Get out.</font>

687
01:01:34,180 --> 01:01:37,420
<font color="yellow">- That's all you have. - You need to come with me.</font>

688
01:01:37,540 --> 01:01:39,820
<font color="yellow">You'll find out we aren't going anywhere nice.</font>

689
01:01:40,940 --> 01:01:42,060
<font color="yellow">Uncle.</font>

690
01:01:43,300 --> 01:01:45,660
<font color="yellow">If that is your fate, so be it.</font>

691
01:01:47,140 --> 01:01:49,140
<font color="yellow">He was such a good boy.</font>

692
01:01:57,860 --> 01:01:59,180
<font color="yellow">I will get revenge.</font>

693
01:01:59,580 --> 01:02:01,700
<font color="yellow">It must be done before we become close.</font>

694
01:02:01,700 --> 01:02:03,540
<font color="yellow">(NASA phone number)</font>

695
01:02:07,980 --> 01:02:10,100
<font color="yellow">Uncles, you got it all wrong.</font>

696
01:02:10,300 --> 01:02:13,980
<font color="yellow">I wanted to ask if I can set up a branch here in Seoul.</font>

697
01:02:15,300 --> 01:02:16,700
<font color="yellow">Uncles.</font>

698
01:02:18,180 --> 01:02:19,500
<font color="yellow">Uncles?</font>

699
01:02:22,500 --> 01:02:23,820
<font color="yellow">Uncle.</font>

700
01:02:30,980 --> 01:02:32,780
<font color="yellow">Aunt?</font>

701
01:02:34,100 --> 01:02:37,180
<font color="yellow">Why do you look so surprised? I'm not banned from visiting.</font>

702
01:02:38,540 --> 01:02:39,820
<font color="yellow">Do you have any food?</font>

703
01:02:40,700 --> 01:02:43,860
<font color="yellow">No? I knew it.</font>

704
01:02:43,900 --> 01:02:46,860
<font color="yellow">I bet you order in all the time because you're rich now.</font>

705
01:02:51,700 --> 01:02:54,980
<font color="yellow">Come inside. I'll cook you something.</font>

706
01:02:55,540 --> 01:02:58,700
<font color="yellow">I'm not a picky eater. I wouldn't mind something grilled.</font>

707
01:03:01,180 --> 01:03:04,260
<font color="yellow">How are Gyeong Mi and Gyeong Sik?</font>

708
01:03:04,660 --> 01:03:07,340
<font color="yellow">- Have you seen them? - I don't care about them.</font>

709
01:03:07,340 --> 01:03:09,340
<font color="yellow">No news is good news.</font>

710
01:03:09,500 --> 01:03:12,300
<font color="yellow">Good riddance, I say. I'm better off without them.</font>

711
01:03:12,500 --> 01:03:15,780
<font color="yellow">Is this where you live? You make money, don't you?</font>

712
01:03:16,060 --> 01:03:18,700
<font color="yellow">I guess good grades get you nowhere.</font>

713
01:03:18,940 --> 01:03:20,380
<font color="yellow">Is it a monthly rent?</font>

714
01:03:23,700 --> 01:03:26,820
<font color="yellow">Get me something to eat. I'm sure you're busy.</font>

715
01:03:27,620 --> 01:03:32,500
<font color="yellow">Next week, we'll look into a few cases everyone can relate to.</font>

716
01:03:32,540 --> 01:03:36,220
<font color="yellow">Thank you. Giving us some valuable legal advice...</font>

717
01:03:36,300 --> 01:03:38,300
<font color="yellow">was lawyer Kim Yoo Na.</font>

718
01:03:38,580 --> 01:03:41,780
<font color="yellow">I hope you have a weekend ruled by common sense.</font>

719
01:03:41,940 --> 01:03:44,700
<font color="yellow">I'll play you a song and after the commercial break,</font>

720
01:03:44,700 --> 01:03:46,780
<font color="yellow">we'll come back with part three.</font>

721
01:03:54,180 --> 01:03:55,700
<font color="yellow">How was that?</font>

722
01:03:56,020 --> 01:03:58,500
<font color="yellow">You should switch jobs. You were awesome.</font>

723
01:03:59,340 --> 01:04:01,180
<font color="yellow">You didn't even listen.</font>

724
01:04:02,300 --> 01:04:05,980
<font color="yellow">You look upset. Shall we have a drink?</font>

725
01:04:08,180 --> 01:04:11,500
<font color="yellow">No. I have to go and see the chicken lady...</font>

726
01:04:11,660 --> 01:04:13,700
<font color="yellow">and I have plans. Maybe next time.</font>

727
01:04:14,420 --> 01:04:15,980
<font color="yellow">See you around.</font>

728
01:04:16,780 --> 01:04:17,940
<font color="yellow">Bye.</font>

729
01:04:25,860 --> 01:04:29,100
<font color="yellow">I'll be packed and gone by the weekend.</font>

730
01:04:29,620 --> 01:04:33,380
<font color="yellow">Very well. I'll inform your landlord.</font>

731
01:04:36,060 --> 01:04:37,260
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

732
01:04:44,820 --> 01:04:47,380
<font color="yellow">What got into you? One trip abroad...</font>

733
01:04:47,380 --> 01:04:49,220
<font color="yellow">and you're acting like a foreigner?</font>

734
01:04:49,300 --> 01:04:52,380
<font color="yellow">I missed you, Boss.</font>

735
01:04:52,860 --> 01:04:55,020
<font color="yellow">You're never at work or at home.</font>

736
01:04:55,340 --> 01:04:56,900
<font color="yellow">Where were you?</font>

737
01:04:57,820 --> 01:04:59,580
<font color="yellow">Packing up to move.</font>

738
01:05:01,740 --> 01:05:04,500
<font color="yellow">You're moving? Your home or business?</font>

739
01:05:04,820 --> 01:05:06,140
<font color="yellow">Both.</font>

740
01:05:06,700 --> 01:05:08,820
<font color="yellow">To overcome my new house phobia.</font>

741
01:05:08,940 --> 01:05:10,820
<font color="yellow">There's no such thing.</font>

742
01:05:16,180 --> 01:05:18,540
<font color="yellow">I got this for you from Canada.</font>

743
01:05:18,660 --> 01:05:21,540
<font color="yellow">I've been carrying it around hoping to meet you.</font>

744
01:05:24,500 --> 01:05:26,820
<font color="yellow">Did you find what you went to look for?</font>

745
01:05:28,060 --> 01:05:30,620
<font color="yellow">Everything. I found everything.</font>

746
01:05:31,220 --> 01:05:33,900
<font color="yellow">You won't believe me even if I told you.</font>

747
01:05:34,740 --> 01:05:37,420
<font color="yellow">I found everything and a boyfriend.</font>

748
01:05:37,420 --> 01:05:40,220
<font color="yellow">In Quebec of all places. It was destiny.</font>

749
01:05:40,220 --> 01:05:42,420
<font color="yellow">Is your destiny handsome?</font>

750
01:05:42,580 --> 01:05:43,900
<font color="yellow">Incredibly.</font>

751
01:05:44,020 --> 01:05:47,060
<font color="yellow">He has large, clear eyes and he served his country.</font>

752
01:05:47,060 --> 01:05:49,220
<font color="yellow">He must be so stubborn.</font>

753
01:05:49,700 --> 01:05:50,860
<font color="yellow">He is.</font>

754
01:05:53,140 --> 01:05:56,420
<font color="yellow">- What? - I know you have low standards.</font>

755
01:05:56,420 --> 01:05:58,860
<font color="yellow">Did you have fun with Mr. Restaurant?</font>

756
01:06:00,260 --> 01:06:04,380
<font color="yellow">I'll introduce him to you one day.</font>

757
01:06:04,380 --> 01:06:07,420
<font color="yellow">I really want you to meet him.</font>

758
01:06:09,220 --> 01:06:10,580
<font color="yellow">Forget it.</font>

759
01:06:11,180 --> 01:06:14,340
<font color="yellow">- Why? - I saw him leave your room.</font>

760
01:06:14,500 --> 01:06:16,060
<font color="yellow">Do what you want.</font>

761
01:06:19,340 --> 01:06:20,340
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

762
01:06:21,740 --> 01:06:24,940
<font color="yellow">Just. I was thinking of old times.</font>

763
01:06:25,700 --> 01:06:29,100
<font color="yellow">Okay. You do as you want with that, too.</font>

764
01:06:30,020 --> 01:06:32,260
<font color="yellow">Take care of yourself, okay?</font>

765
01:06:32,340 --> 01:06:33,500
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

766
01:06:34,020 --> 01:06:36,140
<font color="yellow">You sound like we'll never see each other again.</font>

767
01:06:36,300 --> 01:06:38,980
<font color="yellow">Goodbye, then. I have to meet someone.</font>

768
01:06:38,980 --> 01:06:39,980
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

769
01:06:52,860 --> 01:06:54,580
<font color="yellow">Oh, you again.</font>

770
01:06:54,580 --> 01:06:55,780
<font color="yellow">I'll say.</font>

771
01:06:59,820 --> 01:07:01,500
<font color="yellow">He's a Canadian ghost.</font>

772
01:07:02,780 --> 01:07:04,140
<font color="yellow">That man...</font>

773
01:07:05,580 --> 01:07:07,340
<font color="yellow">was a ghost.</font>

774
01:07:09,780 --> 01:07:11,700
<font color="yellow">I didn't see them for a while.</font>

775
01:07:11,940 --> 01:07:13,980
<font color="yellow">Why have I started seeing them again?</font>

776
01:07:18,980 --> 01:07:20,780
<font color="yellow">Why are you so deep in thought?</font>

777
01:07:21,180 --> 01:07:22,420
<font color="yellow">Hi.</font>

778
01:07:23,340 --> 01:07:24,740
<font color="yellow">I was thinking about Canada.</font>

779
01:07:24,740 --> 01:07:26,300
<font color="yellow">Not about me?</font>

780
01:07:26,300 --> 01:07:28,140
<font color="yellow">I was thinking about Canada,</font>

781
01:07:28,140 --> 01:07:30,580
<font color="yellow">and naturally, I started thinking about you.</font>

782
01:07:30,700 --> 01:07:32,860
<font color="yellow">You said you went there four times with your first love,</font>

783
01:07:33,140 --> 01:07:35,340
<font color="yellow">that you fed your first love beef,</font>

784
01:07:35,340 --> 01:07:38,060
<font color="yellow">and that your first love is still just as pretty.</font>

785
01:07:38,820 --> 01:07:39,980
<font color="yellow">And?</font>

786
01:07:39,980 --> 01:07:42,500
<font color="yellow">So I was thinking...</font>

787
01:07:42,500 --> 01:07:44,820
<font color="yellow">maybe I am that first love.</font>

788
01:07:45,500 --> 01:07:46,540
<font color="yellow">And?</font>

789
01:07:46,540 --> 01:07:48,940
<font color="yellow">And something is off.</font>

790
01:07:49,020 --> 01:07:51,660
<font color="yellow">Then who was that first love that you said you met...</font>

791
01:07:51,660 --> 01:07:53,500
<font color="yellow">during late Joseon?</font>

792
01:07:54,180 --> 01:07:55,300
<font color="yellow">You.</font>

793
01:07:56,340 --> 01:07:57,620
<font color="yellow">Liar.</font>

794
01:07:58,540 --> 01:08:00,500
<font color="yellow">Before we even met...</font>

795
01:08:00,500 --> 01:08:02,300
<font color="yellow">Before I even knew,</font>

796
01:08:03,180 --> 01:08:04,940
<font color="yellow">you had come by.</font>

797
01:08:05,540 --> 01:08:08,500
<font color="yellow">I saw you on the 12th year of King Chuljong's reign.</font>

798
01:08:09,740 --> 01:08:11,500
<font color="yellow">You in the far future.</font>

799
01:08:15,580 --> 01:08:18,500
<font color="yellow">- Liar. - It almost seems like a lie.</font>

800
01:08:21,140 --> 01:08:23,540
<font color="yellow">That's so cool. I'm so excited.</font>

801
01:08:23,700 --> 01:08:25,780
<font color="yellow">It really seems like a lie...</font>

802
01:08:25,780 --> 01:08:28,060
<font color="yellow">that the first love was me.</font>

803
01:08:28,620 --> 01:08:30,820
<font color="yellow">That's right. Then back then...</font>

804
01:08:30,820 --> 01:08:33,180
<font color="yellow">when I made a wish during the first snowfall,</font>

805
01:08:33,620 --> 01:08:34,940
<font color="yellow">was that...</font>

806
01:08:35,500 --> 01:08:37,980
<font color="yellow">how the warrior Kim Shin looked?</font>

807
01:08:38,820 --> 01:08:39,860
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

808
01:08:39,860 --> 01:08:41,860
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

809
01:08:42,300 --> 01:08:44,260
<font color="yellow">I was really curious...</font>

810
01:08:45,300 --> 01:08:47,780
<font color="yellow">about your past that I didn't know.</font>

811
01:08:48,300 --> 01:08:49,780
<font color="yellow">But I got to see you.</font>

812
01:08:49,780 --> 01:08:52,340
<font color="yellow">- Did I look strange? - No. You looked cool.</font>

813
01:08:52,340 --> 01:08:53,780
<font color="yellow">A man from Goryeo.</font>

814
01:09:02,100 --> 01:09:04,380
<font color="yellow">Yes. That's why I'm saying this.</font>

815
01:09:05,900 --> 01:09:09,020
<font color="yellow">I'm saying this because today is just about right.</font>

816
01:09:12,580 --> 01:09:15,340
<font color="yellow">I'm saying this because you are still shining.</font>

817
01:09:17,980 --> 01:09:19,860
<font color="yellow">I'm saying this because...</font>

818
01:09:20,220 --> 01:09:22,300
<font color="yellow">you were that first love.</font>

819
01:09:23,700 --> 01:09:25,700
<font color="yellow">On another day that is just about right,</font>

820
01:09:26,580 --> 01:09:29,100
<font color="yellow">will you be my bride?</font>

821
01:10:18,980 --> 01:10:21,980
<font color="yellow">(Goblin)</font>

822
01:10:22,500 --> 01:10:25,660
<font color="yellow">For a long, long time...</font>

823
01:10:27,860 --> 01:10:29,180
<font color="yellow">Goodbye.</font>

824
01:10:29,580 --> 01:10:30,860
<font color="yellow">Goodbye.</font>

825
01:10:35,420 --> 01:10:37,740
<font color="yellow">Is this our happy ending?</font>

826
01:10:38,980 --> 01:10:39,980
<font color="yellow">That is...</font>

827
01:10:40,740 --> 01:10:42,660
<font color="yellow">the instincts of that moment...</font>

828
01:10:43,380 --> 01:10:44,740
<font color="yellow">and completely...</font>

829
01:10:45,220 --> 01:10:47,500
<font color="yellow">one human being's choice.</font>

830
01:10:51,220 --> 01:10:52,500
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

831
01:10:54,820 --> 01:10:56,700
<font color="yellow">I'm so sorry.</font>

